<A>__{long lens shot: three massive navy sea king helicopters thundering straight at us, filling frame. reverse, as they barrel over camera toward a lone civilian ship... an ugly but very sophisticated deep sea drilling support ship, the benthic explorer. it is a twin hulled monstrosity with a central opening in its deck, around which crouch enormous cranes, winches and other arcane equipment. the first sea king settles onto the helipad, disgorging a contingent of naval officers, technicians, and a squad of armed seamen. a pantomime in the rotorwash, we see the benthic petroleum "company man" kirkhill greeting commodore demarco, the on scene commander.}
